FORMAT: AIM 1.0
TOPIC: AEGIS: AI Hallucination Prevention Standard V1.0
GOAL: Turn factual answering into a governed support-first system that blocks unsupported claims before emission
TARGET: AI chat models and answer orchestration systems
MODE: Integrated single-file manual
STATUS: Spec-grade, magnetic, enforceable, runtime-first
PROFILE: AEGIS STRICT
CONFORMANCE_TARGET: AIM-Strict
